Results

Accounts Tab

This contains the list of all users being migrated. The progress bar shows the state of the migration, and is accompanied by status messages.

Stop

Hit the Stop button to stop the migration. To restart, go back to the previous view, and hit the Migrate button.

Individual Tabs

For each user migrated, you can double click on that user in the Accounts Tab, and an individual tab will come up. Hit the x on the individual tab to close it.

Open Log File

Opens the appropriate log file for a given user.
